OL,3,CShip near the Strait of Hormuz seized
OL,4,Cand brought to Iran, officials say
OL,6,FA ship anchored off the United Arab
OL,7,FEmirates has been seized and taken
OL,8,Ftowards Iran, the British military
OL,9,Fsaid.
OL,11,FThere were no immediate claims of
OL,12,Fresponsibility when the incident
OL,13,Fhappened on Thursday, but a senior
OL,14,FIranian official reiterated his
OL,15,Fcountry's claim to the waterway.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/7
