OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1778803375
OL,3,CShip near the Strait of Hormuz seized
OL,4,Cand brought to Iran, officials say
OL,6,FAnother official said Iran had the
OL,7,Fright to seize oil tankers connected
OL,8,Fto the US. It is unclear who the ships
OL,9,Fbelong to, but British forces who
OL,10,Fflagged the incident are operating in
OL,11,Fthe area.
OL,13,FThursday's incident marked a renewed
OL,14,Fescalation of tensions in shipping
OL,15,Fnear the Strait of Hormuz.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/7
