OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1778803375
OL,3,CShip near the Strait of Hormuz seized
OL,4,Cand brought to Iran, officials say
OL,6,FIran's judiciary spokesperson, Asghar
OL,7,FJahangir, told an Iranian newspaper on
OL,8,FThursday that Iran has the legal right
OL,9,Fto seize oil tankers connected to the
OL,10,FUS in the Strait, and accused
OL,11,FWashington of violating international
OL,12,Fmaritime law and committing piracy.
OL,14,FHe did not explicitly refer to the
OL,15,Ftanker seized on Thursday.
OL,17,FLast week, Iran seized a number of
OL,18,Fships, including a tanker identified
OL,19,Fas the Ocean Koi, saying it was acting
OL,20,Fto protect its oil exports and
OL,21,Finterests.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
