OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1778803375
OL,3,CShip near the Strait of Hormuz seized
OL,4,Cand brought to Iran, officials say
OL,6,FThe seizure comes as US President
OL,7,FDonald Trump met with Chinese leader
OL,8,FXi Jinping on a much-anticipated visit
OL,9,Fto Beijing.
OL,11,FThe White House said both countries
OL,12,Fagreed that the Strait of Hormuz must
OL,13,Fremain open.
