OL,3,CShip near the Strait of Hormuz seized
OL,4,Cand brought to Iran, officials say
OL,6,FElsewhere, Indian authorities also
OL,7,Fconfirmed that an Indian-flagged cargo
OL,8,Fship sank off the coast of Oman after
OL,9,Fan attack sparked a fire on board.
OL,11,FThe vessel, the Haji Ali, was
OL,12,Ftravelling from Somalia to Sharjah
OL,13,Fwhen it was struck on Wednesday.
OL,15,FAll 14 Indian crew members were
OL,16,Frescued by Oman's coast guard.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/7
