PN,31406
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1778803375
OL,3,CShip near the Strait of Hormuz seized
OL,4,Cand brought to Iran, officials say
OL,6,FIndia's foreign ministry called the
OL,7,Fincident "unacceptable" and condemned
OL,8,Fcontinued attacks on commercial
OL,9,Fshipping, without identifying who
OL,10,Fattacked the ship.
OL,12,FMeanwhile, Iran said it will not enter
OL,13,Fmore talks with the US unless
OL,14,FWashington meets five conditions,
OL,15,Fincluding paying reparations for the
OL,16,Fwar and accepting Iran's sovereignty
OL,17,Fover the Strait of Hormuz, Iran's
OL,18,Fsemiofficial Fars news agency reported.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/7
