OL,3,CShip near the Strait of Hormuz seized
OL,4,Cand brought to Iran, officials say
OL,6,FThe White House is again unlikely to
OL,7,Faccept those demands, especially
OL,8,Fagreeing that Iran controls the
OL,9,Fwaterway, which was open to
OL,10,Finternational traffic before the war.
